Prebon watched the battle at the Iron fist when he noticed a strategic
mistake Zardus had made.

"With most of the alliance at the Cybertronian Fire thier base should be an
easy target."

Prebons plan was to take the alliance base and pick the survivors from the
battle off one by one.

"Ignatius and Slayer will be our air support, Blaze, Bullet, Hammer and I
will go in from the ground. Be prepared for anything, just because the
gestaults aren't there doesn't mean that it'll be an easy target."

Bullet, Blaze and Hammer loaded thier weapons, readied thier rockets, and
went airborn using rocketpacks from the supply room. Prebon followed his
troops with a glint in his eye. Slayer and Ignatius were to follow, once the
first group was in position the others would follow.
